snippet.title: Pandora Plays
snippet.description:
Welcome to Pandora Plays where I play series from the very beginning and try out as many games as I can to give you my first impression, reaction and informal review! 

UPDATE: Get ready for MORE Reaction Videos to MULTIPLY the Entertainment! 

Get ready for Movie Trailer Reactions, Funny Videos, Unboxing Events.. It's all coming up on Pandora Plays!


[ Games in Progress... ]
1. Amnesia, A Machine For Pigs
2. The Adventure Pals
3. Diablo II
4. Enigmatis: Ghost of Maple Creek
5. F.E.A.R.
6. Kingdom Rush Origins
7. Mad Max
8. Resident Evil 2 (2010)
9. The Walking Dead, Season 2

[ Completed Games ]
1. Amnesia, The Dark Descent
2. DreadOut 1
3. Five Nights at Freddy's (all 5, inc. Sister Location)
4. Resident Evil 1
5. SOMA
6. The Walking Dead, Season 1
7. The Walking Dead, 400 Days

Stay tuned for ALL the Games, ALL the Time.
